# Styling

## Rules

- Use Tailwind utilities in `className`.
- Use CSS only in `src/index.css`.
- Use semantic design tokens only.
- Prefer existing tokens/utilities before creating new ones.

## Forbidden

- Component CSS files
- CSS Modules
- `App.css`
- Arbitrary values (`[...]`)
- Brand/custom color names (`apple-*`, `slate-*`, `gray-*`)
- Raw colors outside `src/index.css`
- Layout wrappers like `mx-auto max-w-* px-*`

```tsx
// ❌ bg-apple-bg text-[17px] top-[53px] mx-auto max-w-xl px-4
// ✅ bg-surface text-body-lg top-site-header container
```

## Color Tokens

### Surface
`surface` · `surface-elevated` · `surface-muted` · `fill`

### Text
`foreground` · `foreground-muted` · `foreground-subtle`

### Structure
`border` · `separator`

### Action
`primary` · `primary-hover` · `on-primary` · `link`

### Status
`success` · `info`

### Accent
`accent-purple` · `accent-orange`

### Neutral
`neutral-50` → `neutral-900`

> Colors exist only in the PALETTE section of `src/index.css`.

## Layout

```tsx
<Container backgroundClassName sectionClassName>
```

Inner content:

```tsx
className="container"
```

## Tokens

`--container-max`
`--container-max-md`
`--spacing-site-header`
`--min-height-hero`
`--text-body-lg`
`--scale-press`

## Extensions

| Add | Use |
|------|------|
| Token | `@theme` |
| Utility | `@utility` |
| Global styles | `@layer base` |

## Patterns

```tsx
['base', condition && 'variant']
  .filter(Boolean)
  .join(' ')
```

- Use variant helpers.
- Expose styling overrides through `*ClassName`.